extendedInfo.description: With the competition of getting into a good college getting tougher every year, it is important to get good SAT and SAT 2 scores. This app lets you keep track of all of your practice test and official scores for both the SAT 1 and SAT 2 (all subjects included) and display all of the scores on one page. Using this app, you will be able to easily find your strengths and weaknesses and conquer the SAT/SAT 2. Bonus Feature: A raw score calculator is also included in this app to make finding the raw scores for practice tests as simple and painless as possible.
